# 📈 StockVision AI

StockVision AI is a web application that predicts the next day's stock closing price using Machine Learning.
Users can search for a stock, view company information, analyze historical price data, and receive a predicted closing price along with a simple
Buy, Hold, or Sell recommendation. The frontend is built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, while the backend uses Flask and Scikit-learn for prediction.
Stock data is fetched using the Finnhub API and Yahoo Finance. This project was developed to understand how machine learning models can be
integrated with web applications and to gain hands-on experience with full-stack development.